PROPERTY DETAILS
High quality office/showroom and training facility plus a workshop separately leased all adjoining a fully sealed corner asphalt yard.

RPD: 4 Titles. Lots 23-26 on SP 160465
CTR 50539200 - 50539203
Total Land Area: 4150m2
Dimensions: Frontage to McGregor Rd - 107 meters* Frontage to Mac Peak Crescent - 39 meters*
Title Encumbrances: Nil. There are no easements on the property.
Zone: Industry - Low Impact

TENANCY: There is currently a casual mth-mth tenant in place.

DEVELOPMENT OPPORTUNITY: The total site could take up to 2000m2* of commercial/industrial development subject to council approvals and design. The site is ideal for further small and larger warehousing and or strata development.

IMPROVEMENTS: 
The improvements are situated on only two titles:

+ Main warehouse 533m2 comprising a high clearance zinculum framed construction shed of 290m2 plus a showroom of 90m2 plus mezzanine offices/training rooms of 153m2. There are 3 high clearance and one low clearance roller doors.

+ Adjoining is a low clearance lunch room, kitchen and lock up store of 79m2

+ There is a separate 3 bay high clearance metal clad storage shed adjoining of 128m2

+ Approved 38m2 covered washbay.

+ Total floor area is 778m2

+ Lots 23 & 24 or 225 McGregor Rd (corner) are fully bitumen sealed and fenced.

* approx.
** subject to council approvals & design
